00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:48.000
What does it feel like for someone like you, who has played on the local pitches of your town

00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:53.000
and for a lot of small local teams, to walk out onto the San Siro pitch, score a goal and hear the crowd roar.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:02.000
